               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18490507-name-558" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18490507-name-558" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18490507-name-558" type="surname" value="SMITH"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18490507-name-558" type="given" value="BENJAMIN"></interp>BENJAMIN SMITH</persName>
                  </hi> On 3d April, a person came for an order and sample for Messrs. Mumford—I believe it was the prisoner—I gave him a sample, half a pint of malt.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
